Resolution Committee.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Financial Commission notes that it will not be able to process any new complaints from EGMarkets clients\u2019, following its expulsion from the Financial Commission as of the date of this announcement and moving forward.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As Financial Commission is an industry-supported self-regulatory organization (SRO) our enforcement of member compliance is reflected entirely within our membership standings where a firm\u2019s integrity and adherence to rules must be strictly upheld in order for membership to be maintained.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For more information about Financial Commission membership requirements, please contact us or visit <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">www.financialcommission.com.co<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false,"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"html"}]},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>April 15th, 2022, Financial Commission, a leading external dispute resolution (EDR) organization catering to the financial services industry today announces that it has expelled EGMarkets from membership in the organization following a breach of contractual obligations. In order to maintain membership with the Financial Commission, member firms must strictly adhere to membership rules and all [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false,"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"html"}]},"author":2,"featured_media":125168,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[14,12,15,16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-125167","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-commission-news","category-company-news-news-events","category-press-release","category-p